@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
abstract class Diagnosis {
  +Date phone
  -float duration
  -float total
  +calculateName()
  +deleteCreatedat()
}
class Patient {
  #Date level
  #long note
  +boolean amount
  -long createdAt
  #double quantity
  +updateQuantity()
  +updatePhone()
}
class Appointment {
  #double quantity
  +int type
  +double status
  +Date email
  +calculateTotal()
  +sendDuration()
  +findType()
  +validateTotal()
}
class Ward {
  -double active
  -long duration
  +updateStatus()
  +calculateEmail()
  +updateScore()
  +findTotal()
}
Ward --* Diagnosis
Appointment --o Ward
Patient --> Appointment : "0..1"
note right of Diagnosis : Healthcare domain
@enduml